data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!! Welcome Home!!! This magnificent 2-story  ,4 bdrm, 3 bath,home boasts 3131  sq ft of luxurious living space. Spacious rooms to include two living rooms, two dining rooms, and a game room/loft, perfect for entertaining. The kitchen features a family-sized breakfast bar, granite countertops, modern appliances, and a massive walk-in pantry. Entertain family ,friends or just  sit by the fireplace and enjoy the evenings in your cozy kitchen/living/ dining combo.Large windows that allow natural sunlight ,and high ceilings also accentuate this open floor plan. Spacious is an understatement that describes the master suite it's impressive size with a walk-in closet, double vanities, a luxurious Jacuzzi garden tub, and separate shower WOW!!! Additional bedrooms, complete the upstairs ,now let's not forget one bedroom is downstairs this home has it all. Great location ,great schools, move in ready , and PRICED TO SELL .The home is a must see schedule your appointment today.
